            div.flex.flex-col.gap-10.m-auto(class='h-[300px]')
                div.text-4xl.font-bold Us Vs Them; A Comprehensive Analysis
                div.text-gray-300.text-sm Agentflix makes marketing more cost effective and easy than ever thought possible. By combining and improving on existing techniques, we incorporate all our features in one dedicated space online free for users to explore. It's more efficient than billboards and flyers!
