                        img(src="/images/next.svg")
                img(src="/images/image4.png")
        div
            div.grid.grid-cols-2.gap-4.px-40
                img(src="/images/image3.png")
                div.flex.flex-col.gap-5.m-auto(class='h-[300px]')
                    div(class='text-[#FF7F5C] font-bold') Our Feature
                    div.text-4xl.font-bold Take your career to a new level
                    div.text-gray-300.text-sm Whether starting your career or a seasoned professional, integrating yourself to the digital world is key to unlocking a new audience of potential clients. To achieve this, there needs to be a dedicated platform for real estate. Agentflix fixes the scattered and outdated marketing methods of real estate and connects clients with agents easier.
                    a.py-2.px-4.flex.gap-2.w-fit.rounded-full(href="../auth/register" class="bg-[#1B8D9C]")
